data.description: WELCOME HOME to Maplewood! This outstanding villa truly appears and lives as a single-family residence with a total of 2243 sq ft of living space! The villa has been meticulously maintained and was professionally painted last year. It features gorgeous crown molding throughout the entire home and has been tastefully furnished. It offers spacious bedrooms, two of which have ensuite bathrooms with granite counter tops, vessel sinks and plentiful closet space. Enjoy a large eat in kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, loads of cabinet space and beautiful granite countertops. The open kitchen allows you to sit at the bar or relax and dine in the living room/dining area while never missing a conversation with guests and family. Want to have quiet reading or tv time while enjoying the view outdoors? Then the large enclosed lanai with floor to ceiling windows is the room for you. Enjoy sunny days while relaxing on the outdoor paver deck under the roll out awning and end each day grilling and relaxing in the hot tub. Buying a second home? This villa has what you need while you are away with lockable accordion shutters on all windows,  ADT security system, automated sprinkler system
